customValues.infoDesc:
While Boyfriend runs from the animatronic he runs and hides in a room and locks the door. While thinking he is safe, an arcade turns on. Revealing a game called "Bunny Farm". A strangely familiar bear shows itself in the arcade machine.






Based on the Walten Files 3 "BunnyFarm" by Martin Walls.
